  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Porky Pig ventures to Dry Gultch Haunted Theme Park and while staying there, falls asleep. He dreams up a nightmare, staring all sorts of fiendish foes including a very annoying Daffy Duck of various sorts. Venturing through ghostly mansions, haunted woods and a strange otherworld that plays the music from Terry Gilliam's Brazil!",
